e":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4dcaac488cad4d6cdcec74974ab76017dee0453","tid":540934,"uid":60545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"65ef3625afa3458db8e2e341b79d28dc86769ee2","tid":540934,"uid":11920,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e55fd830ffb5cc7130a7a5e926340f43a09ea1fc","tid":540934,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T03:13:57.000Z","msg":"普通話考變考西隧巴士路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T03:22:10.000Z","msg":"仲要九龍經西隧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n住新界嗰D真係唔會識答<br />\n除非係巴膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T03:24:16.000Z","msg":"住九龍都唔識啦，仲要講特質？有乜特質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T03:24:55.000Z","msg":"標準答案：973<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739a6269974bd0a1c74b84a56ac523e475ca2b61","tid":540934,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T03:25:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea9e37b8f19f8402a72aa198070a3c4d21bc9751","tid":540934,"uid":5686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"582e73be8f48d727915739e0f2b47fc77d5478e6","tid":540934,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"529624ceade04d05314314dc96e6cdfa3516b370","tid":540934,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T03:05:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T03:18:21.000Z","msg":"考試內容都要合理啩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T03:27:41.000Z","msg":"是但搵個蝗國生問下點邊條巴士線係啱先啦,<br />\n問100個100個都死.<br />\n<br />\n(但係人地唔駛考喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 港豬有排受呀)<br />\n<br />\n蝗國人代代都考IELTS/TOEFL 移民/去外國讀書,<br />\n你班港豬就考唔到蝗話試就無得畢業, 讀多四年之後同四年前考唔到DSE果個人學歷一樣，<br />\n仲要無腦到俾CCTVB SPIN 兩野個論點就由不平等要你修/考蝗話試變大學生應唔應該講粗口。<br />\n我係蝗國人的話都覺得，